@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Upcoming Features";
}

<div class="container mt-5">
    <h1 class="mb-4">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

    <p>We are continuously working to improve the Agri-Energy platform. Below are some exciting features you can look forward to in the near future:</p>

    <ul class="list-group list-group-flush mt-4">
        <li class="list-group-item">
            <strong>Chat/Discussion:</strong>
            <br />
            A community-driven space where farmers and green energy professionals can connect, share knowledge, and discuss best practices.
        </li>

        <li class="list-group-item">
            <strong>Payment Inputs and Payment Options:</strong>
            <br />
            Integration of secure payment methods to facilitate transactions related to products, services, and funding.
        </li>

        <li class="list-group-item">
            <strong>Redesigned Responsive UI:</strong>
            <br />
            A more modern, user-friendly, and mobile-optimized interface to enhance the overall user experience.
        </li>

        <li class="list-group-item">
            <strong>Educational and Training Resources:</strong>
            <br />
            Access to online courses, webinars, and workshops focusing on the integration of green energy technologies in agriculture.
            <br />
            Learn about the benefits and practical steps for adopting renewable energy on your farm.
        </li>

        <li class="list-group-item">
            <strong>Project Collaboration and Funding Opportunities:</strong>
            <br />
            A platform to connect farmers and energy experts for joint green energy projects.
            <br />
            Find information on available grants, subsidies, and other funding sources for sustainable initiatives.
        </li>
    </ul>

    <div class="mt-5">
        <a asp-controller="Dashboard" asp-action="EmployeeDashboard" class="btn btn-secondary">
            ← Back to Dashboard
        </a>
    </div>
</div>

